{
  "stem": "8892.3",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I just walk towards the barrack.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And double portion of food was in my hand, and some soup or some bread.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I don't even know what.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And-- but, but noise and the sound was so tremendous that my sister did not sleep.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And, of course, after that, she didn't let me go back to the kitchen that, you know, she let me alone.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the bombing was so bad that they had to empty the camp-- the Plaszow, the concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And then they shipped us back to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Again, we going.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But, you know, we are getting back to the cattle car.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We don't know where we going.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "That's one thing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We didn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But when we arrived, we knew.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And when we arrived in July and got off the cattle car, the smell was so intense, that's when we realized.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "We did-- I mean, we really actually didn't see the crematorium or smell that till then.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Because in Krakau, there was selection in there, too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But they shot you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They shot you.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They shot you anytime they feel like to.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "They counted you.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And if you were, I don't know-- they decide every tenth is going to be-- get out of the line, and they shoot you.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "They just shot you right there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "But we didn't see no crematorium.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Or we didn't see the mass grave or nothing because it was in front of us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "But they were very, very cruel-- very cruel.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And when we get back to Auschwitz, then we feel, this is it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Sure enough, again, we going to go through.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Didn't shave us that time because we still didn't have no hair anyway.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "But we going to the shower.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
